Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.17,0:06:47.67,AnneHappy_Main,HIBARI,0,0,0,,Nói mới nhớ, \Ntớ vẫn chưa biết tên cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.18,AnneHappy_Main,HANAKO,0,0,0,,À, phải rồi nhỉ!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.39,AnneHappy_Main,HANAKO,0,0,0,,E hèm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:53.85,AnneHappy_Main,HANAKO,0,0,0,,Tớ tên là Hanakoizumi An.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:58.73,sign_7829_Hanakoizumi_Anne,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(730,1)\pos(1216,76)}Ha\Nna\N\N\N\Nko\N\N\N\Ni\Nzu\Nmi\N\N\NAn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:57.85,AnneHappy_Main,HANAKO,0,0,0,,Hồi Sơ Trung, mọi người hay gọi tớ là Anne.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:58.73,AnneHappy_Main,HANAKO,0,0,0,,Rất mong cậu giúp đỡ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:01.94,AnneHappy_Main,HIBARI,0,0,0,,Tớ cũng mong cậu giúp đỡ, Hanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:02.98,AnneHappy_Main,HANAKO,0,0,0,,Hể?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.19,AnneHappy_Main,HANAKO,0,0,0,,Hanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.61,sign_8080_Hanako,TEXT,0,0,0,,Ha
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.61,sign_8080_Hanako,TEXT,570,530,0,,na
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.61,sign_8080_Hanako,TEXT,950,20,0,,ko
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:10.32,AnneHappy_Main,HIBARI,0,0,0,,Nếu tớ là Hibari, thì cậu là Hanako còn gì?
